  "acceptance_criteria": [
    "Task cards, map selection, district list, and right inspector must agree on the active object and currently relevant action.",
    "Route, obligation, risk, and focus overlays must be opt-in or phase-relevant; unrelated lines must not clutter the default player view.",
    "Map legend and labels must explain what visible lines and highlights mean in the current phase, using player-language terms rather than debug or read-model jargon.",
    "The strategic map may remain low-fidelity, but it must present as a decision map rather than a decorative or engineering diagram.",
    "Map interaction must not introduce new authoritative simulation state or bypass read-model boundaries."
  ],
